	8) Find duplicate in an array of N+1 Integers

  Link: https://leetcode.com/problems/find-the-duplicate-number/description/

  Implementation:

  class Solution {
    public int findDuplicate(int[] arr) {
        Set<Integer> set = new HashSet<>();
        for(int num : arr){
            if(set.contains(num))
                return num;
            set.add(num);
        }
        return -1;
    }
}


Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(n)
